    <item>
      <title>巴西参议院推进碳市场监管法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/brazil-senate-advances-bill-for-regulated-carbon-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西参议院周三批准了一项法案，巴西距离建立一个受监管的碳市场离实现减排和扩大森林面积的目标又近了一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/brazil-senate-advances-bill-for-regulated-carbon-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 22:40:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>霍楚尔计划恢复纽约市拥堵收费计划，收费 9 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/hochul-plans-to-revive-nyc-congestion-pricing-plan-with-9-toll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州长凯西·霍楚尔计划恢复对进入曼哈顿大部分地区的司机征收拥堵费。几个月前，她突然在原定实施日期前取消了这项 15 美元的收费，理由是这项收费会给工薪家庭和小企业带来压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/hochul-plans-to-revive-nyc-congestion-pricing-plan-with-9-toll</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 22:02:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉拥抱习近平引发特朗普对华政策冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-13/brazil-s-embrace-of-china-for-economic-growth-tests-trump-tariff-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统希望北京帮助该国经济发展。这一策略可能会与特朗普发生冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-13/brazil-s-embrace-of-china-for-economic-growth-tests-trump-tariff-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 22:00:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉希望在不激怒唐纳德·特朗普的情况下拉拢习近平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-13/lula-quiere-cortejar-a-xi-jinping-sin-enfadar-a-donald-trump-m3gfd34x</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西寻求北京帮助其经济发展，这可能会引发与特朗普的对抗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-13/lula-quiere-cortejar-a-xi-jinping-sin-enfadar-a-donald-trump-m3gfd34x</guid>
