    <item>
      <title>卢拉和习近平的拥抱是对特朗普对华政策的首次考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-13/abraco-de-lula-e-xi-e-primeiro-teste-da-politica-de-trump-para-a-china-m3gfd33i</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统期待北京​​帮助其国家的经济发展。这一策略可能会与特朗普发生冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-13/abraco-de-lula-e-xi-e-primeiro-teste-da-politica-de-trump-para-a-china-m3gfd33i</guid>
